/F1 11 Tf 50 428 Td (integrates PERT, CPM and Gantt chart planning to calculate expected duration,) Tj
/F1 11 Tf 50 413 Td (critical path, slack and schedule risk.) Tj
/F1 11 Tf 50 391 Td (The project includes user authentication, project history tracking, task) Tj
